{"tid":1583891,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[認真分析檢討Po][行動]討論著黑衫&癱瘓對家文宣手法","createTime":"2019-09-21T00:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T01:21:18.000Z","uid":63045,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"48efc56a353ef7828db648ed4f7576f0feef6982","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:34:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1.觀察</span><br />\n發覺對家好鍾意用一種手法：就係將示威者歸類，再邊緣化，小眾化，將示威同市民切割<br />\n例如2014稱呼做黃絲<br />\n依加叫做黑衣人<br />\n泰國叫黃衫軍<br />\n法國叫黃背心<br />\n<br />\n之後不停用假新聞抹黑著黑衫既人，嚴厲對待黑衣人，等啲游離支持者同黑衫劃清界線，同埋揾人著住黑衫去破壞示威者國際形象<br />\n<br />\n聽過啲無腦藍絲同事係街見到人著黑衫都對條友有偏見，話人係示威者，原因係對家文宣都不斷叫示威者做黑衣人，大陸演練又係揾黑衣人做target<br />\n<br />\n再諗番起前排個幾位成日Twitter開po既外國人，係咁建議我地唔好再用Hong Kong Protesters, 要用HongKonger去稱呼自己<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 建議</span><br />\n有兩個方法應對，Be water<br />\n一係大家乜色衫都著，二係每次著唔同色既衫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 效果</span><br />\n1. 對家超過一半文宣要從新做過，打亂現行緊既計劃<br />\n2. 向外展示示威係市民訴求，大家都係平民，有咩事就係警察/黑社會打平民<br />\n3. 對家無得輕易target 示威者，草木皆兵<br />\n<br />\n記住，我地打長期戰，要不停檢討同埋變通，用死一招對方點要會拆到，佢改善唔到自己形象，唯有就令示威者形象比佢差，掩蓋咗佢，14年其中一個敗因都係對家出依招<br />\n<br />\n當然有啲活動例如十一大家認為有需要，都可以照著黑色，但其他活動就以平民裝，咩色都著<br />\n<br />\n一齊轉個靚彎等班垃圾重新諗過計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7033e91d6abc76414b1f5d65686c090190bafd","tid":1583891,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:34:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"b1bcceebc1c96edfebc8d119cfdc9b2583ec0735","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:35:00.000Z","msg":"[連登平行世界]知道有BirdFoldingChallenge既請舉手<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583663</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推"},{"pid":"5cad99e827762c1c46eeff32ce101c80dbdfb0c2","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:35:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2745b0c8cb89ea3791cbc5fce5e46cba93fb87dc","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7f1026466305beec4b5a1fdd472b3ef6e1e4731f","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:35:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e9eb2f94930ecaf53e0529b529b04a4b95248d3a","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:35:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94625b69c4be047e4c5fa0fc1dc756bc4a45cea6","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:36:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"25301efdcf97e08ed12700f9817a0e6aae072d82","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:36:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ba018076c276d73d045ae6654a5295240af7888","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:36:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"754f096a739aa24e8851ce2692aea4d22de18d48","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:36:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00008f2653b5d21913497b7fb82153b3901a6e3c","tid":1583891,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:36:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42ca68ccd6ed8a8239bf8bf41f1be184cf659fac","tid":1583891,"uid":272569,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:37:07.000Z","msg":"唔係唔著黑衫，係要令更多人日日黑衫"},{"pid":"c6bab1415e77c6bfa15c2dda6d50a4318ac0ce08","tid":1583891,"uid":63464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T00:37:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc0616051cb72a5a293a978a68eac4146415a